name: KFC Le Quest

reviews.text: Flies flying around and each table has 1 literally. Also their new smokey burger is super dry. Chicken also stretchy cant bite off easily.
Friendly staff. We ordered takeaway and upon reaching home we saw this message. Thanks the staff for taking time to write the note on Mother's Day. Best service ever received! Well done.

The lady staff/manager at the counter, wearing a cap, handled the crowd with professionalism. She proactively informed customers that their orders would take some time due to the chicken still being cooked. Meanwhile, she ensured that the other items were served promptly. Despite being busy with the orders, she managed the restaurant smoothly, keeping the tables clean and well-maintained. Date:12/11/2024, 3.47pm.
